/**
 * @defgroup osal_stdio_api osal_stdio API
 * @ingroup osal_family_group
 *
 * @brief Low-level OSAL standard I/O abstraction.
 *
 * @details
 * The `osal_stdio` module provides portable low-level standard I/O primitives
 * through the Operating System Abstraction Layer.
 *
 * It is responsible for standard stream access, stream reads and writes,
 * flushing, error-state queries, end-of-file queries, and injectable standard
 * I/O services.
 */
